钱的目的不就是让自己开心吗？用钱买开心真的很有必要呀！", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "蝎子的这些年", "author_id": "b09b02bb96e527713864bda128ae26eb", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "xiao-shan-pang", "headline": "自由价更高", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "713766798", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "713766798", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "买奢侈品还谈什么必不必要啊，必要那就是必需品了", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "爱喝拿铁的榴莲", "author_id": "0cde5d89f083405c37f5bb388df985c2", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "xiao-shan-pang", "headline": "自由价更高", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "713765671", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "713765671", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "“把这些看成奢侈品的人”？不管谁看它也是奢侈品。不是因为有钱人可以随便买，对他们来说就不是奢侈品了", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "爱喝拿铁的榴莲", "author_id": "0cde5d89f083405c37f5bb388df985c2", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "jiang-lan-du", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "714571797", "reply_comment_id": "714210919", "reply_root_comment_id": "713765671", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你定义的是狭义上的奢侈品，我说的是广义上的奢侈品。既然讲到定义，那要严格按照定义来，你觉得奢侈品是价值/品质最高的东西，那么最高的意思是只有一个，那难道其他稍高的东西就不是奢侈品了吗？所以你想说明啥？来科普奢侈品的定义？可能是贫穷限制了你的想想，人家富人真可能不觉得是奢侈品。不要为了杠而杠好嘛？", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "江澜嘟", "author_id": "6c4c4bed9c023d0376e2d8689776bb39", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xiao-shan-pang", "headline": "自由价更高", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "714210919", "reply_comment_id": "714030367", "reply_root_comment_id": "713765671", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "两块钱可以买一瓶矿泉水，有的几百几千，难道不是奢侈品吗。几百块钱的化妆品你肯定是你的正常消费，但是几百块钱的水呢", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "爱喝拿铁的榴莲", "author_id": "0cde5d89f083405c37f5bb388df985c2", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xiao-shan-pang", "headline": "自由价更高", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "714184409", "reply_comment_id": "714030367", "reply_root_comment_id": "713765671", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "奢侈品(Luxury)在国际上被定义为“一种超出人们生存与发展需要范围的，具有独特、稀缺、珍奇等特点的消费品”，又称为非生活必需品。<br>奢侈品在经济学上讲，指的是价值/品质关系比值最高的产品。从另外一个角度上看，奢侈品又是指无形价值/有形价值关系比值最高的产品。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "爱喝拿铁的榴莲", "author_id": "0cde5d89f083405c37f5bb388df985c2", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jiang-lan-du", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "714030367", "reply_comment_id": "713765671", "reply_root_comment_id": "713765671", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你觉得，不管谁看它都是奢侈品，那么说明奢侈品是绝对的不是相对的，那请你说出满足什么条件就是绝对的奢侈品呢？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "江澜嘟", "author_id": "6c4c4bed9c023d0376e2d8689776bb39", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}]